# Immediate Goal

Run discovery interviews on the top domain candidates and define a **forced wedge**:

1. first user  
2. first painful recurring decision  
3. first domain  
4. what “better” means in session 1  
5. how we will know in 2–4 weeks if it is working  

Until that is clear from evidence — not only from internal discussion — no major technical decisions, expansion decisions, or multi-domain architecture work should be made.

